OL,6,FThe council added that the incident
OL,7,Fwas "unacceptable and this matter will
OL,8,Fbe thoroughly investigated to ensure
OL,9,Fthe correct outcome."
OL,11,FBut Mr Wroz is not the only one who
OL,12,Fhas contacted Denbighshire County
OL,13,FCouncil with concerns and complaints
OL,14,Fabout their recycling system.
OL,16,FIn June the council introduced a new
OL,17,Fwaste system which has cost #22
OL,18,Fmillion. The system requires county
OL,19,Fresidents to separate their recycling
OL,20,Fwaste into different boxes or bags.
