OL,6,FIn an interview, Tony Ward,
OL,7,FDenbighshire County Council's
OL,8,FCorporate Director of Economy and
OL,9,FEnvironment admitted that it is not
OL,10,Fpossible to recycle any items that
OL,11,Fhave been mixed with food.
OL,13,FHe said: "What we saw in the first few
OL,14,Fweeks, we had large areas of the
OL,15,Fcounty who were getting missed
OL,16,Fcollections.
