OL,3,CWelsh Council apologises after binman
OL,4,Cthrew batteries in resident's hedge
OL,6,F"Some had missed collections, week
OL,7,Fafter week, there was a build up of
OL,8,Fwaste on the streets. We had to
OL,9,Frespond to them, we can't just leave
OL,10,Fwaste out on the streets.
OL,12,F"We had a choice between collecting
OL,13,Fthe waste in a commingled way or not
OL,14,Fcollecting it at all. We thought the
OL,15,Fright thing to do was to collect the
OL,16,Fwaste.
OL,18,FAccording to Merfyn Parry who has been
OL,19,Fa councillor in Denbighshire for over
OL,20,Fa decade, some are still waiting for
OL,21,Ftheir bins to be collected since May.
