OL,6,FThe council has invested an additional
OL,7,F#1.3 million to try to solve some of
OL,8,Fthe problems that have occurred. On
OL,9,FMonday changes to the county
OL,10,Fcollection rounds will begin in order
OL,11,Fto try to improve the effectiveness of
OL,12,Fthe system.
OL,14,FMr Ward added: "Some people have been
OL,15,Fhaving inconsistent service for some
OL,16,Fpeople it's been worse than others and
OL,17,Ffor some people it's been better than
OL,18,Fothers some people have never had a
OL,19,Fmissed collection.
